title: Chic Luxury Boutique Midrise!  Washer Dryer Incl!
posting_body: ['Discover the height of attainable elegance.', 'A quick stroll through pedestrian-friendly streets, just beyond Downtown will take you to Dallas’ most vibrant boutique apartment community.', 'Conveniently housed next to Knox-Henderson, and with easy access to Uptown and West Village, the energy of the city is felt as a reverberation of fine dining, entertainment, and access to a limitless lifestyle.', 'Experience urban living at its finest.', 'Community Features....', 'Athletic Center with Cardio Theater and Free Weights', 'Business Lounge with Private Conference Room', 'Pet Park and Dog Washing Station', 'Resident Lounge and Demonstration Kitchen', 'Multiple Covered Outdoor Entertaining Areas with Wi-Fi and media', 'Grilling Stations and Fire Pits', 'Package Acceptance and 24/7 Package Concierge', 'Fully Equipped Bike Storage with Bike Repair Station', 'Conditioned Interior Corridors', 'Multi-Level Parking Garage with Elevator Access', 'Electric Car Charging Stations', 'Resident Storage Unit*', 'Lobby with Complimentary Starbucks and Serving Kitchen', 'Uber-Sheik Swimming Pool with Tanning Ledge', 'Pets Welcome', 'Apartment Features....', 'Recessed Lighting in Kitchen, Dining Areas, and Bathrooms', 'Custom Carpet', 'Ceramic Tile in Bathrooms', 'Butlers Pantry', 'Modern Open-Concept Floor Plans with City Views', 'Bathrooms with Double Vanities and Walk-In Showers', 'Juliet Balcony*', 'Mud Bench', 'Private Yard*', 'Floor to Ceiling Windows with Solar Shades', 'Ceramic tile in all baths', 'Wood Flooring in Living Areas', 'Custom Kitchen Island with Waterfall Edge', 'Granite Countertops with Stone-Tile Backsplash and Farm-Style Sink', 'Bathrooms with Quartz Countertops and Oval Soaking Tubs', 'Stackable Washer and Dryer', 'Energy-Efficient Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Please Call Desiree with DASH Realty', 'show contact info', 'Mention ad 871']
